<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
  <title>Portal GeneXus | O guia do desenvolvedor GeneXus.</title>
  
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'normalize.min' %>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'main' %>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'jquery.wysiwyg' %>
  
  <%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "rails" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "jquery.wysiwyg" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "wysiwyg.image" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "wysiwyg.link" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "wysiwyg.table" %>
  
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  
  <link href="http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Raleway:100|Amethysta|Sofia|Quicksand:300,400,700|Quattrocento+Sans" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
  <script type="text/javascript">
  	$(document).ready(function(){
  		$(".loading").css("display", "none");
		$(".notice").css("display", "none");
  	});
  	function showLoading() {
  		$(".loading").css("display", "");
  	}
  	function hideLoading() {
  		$(".loading").css("display", "none");
  	}
  	function showNotice(msg) {
		$(document).ready(function(){
			$("#flash_notice").html('<p class="notice">' + msg + '</p>');
			$(".notice").css("display", "");
			setTimeout("$('.notice').css('display', 'none')", 2000);
		});
  	}
  </script>
</head>
<body>
<div class="header-container">
	<header class="wrapper clearfix">
		<h1 class="title">Portal GeneXus.</h1>
    	</header>
    	
    	<nav>
		<ul>
			<li class="inicio">
				<%=link_to "Início", {:controller => "page", :action => "inicio"}, {:title=>"Portal GeneXus| O guia do desenvolvedor GeneXus"} %>
			</li>
			<li class="artigos">
				<%=link_to "Artigos", articles_path, {:title=>"Portal GeneXus| Base de Conhecimentos"} %>
			</li>
			<li class="ideologia">
				<%=link_to "Ideologia", {:controller => "page", :action => "ideologia"}, {:title=>"Portal GeneXus| A idéia por trás do código"} %>
			</li>
			<li class="equipe">
				<%=link_to "Equipe", {:controller => "page", :action => "equipe"}, {:title=>"Portal DevGeX | Equipe Portal GeneXus"} %>
			</li>
			<li class="downloads">
				<a href="#" title="Portal DevGeX | Downloads">Downloads</a>
			</li>
			<li class="contato">
				<a href="/contato" title="Portal GeneXus| Entre em contato conosco" >Contato</a>
			</li>
			<% if logged_in? %>
				<% if current_user and current_user.profile.id == 1%>
					<li class="novoartigo">
						<%= link_to "Novo Artigo", new_article_path %>
					</li>
				<% end %>
				<li class="profile">
					<%= link_to "Profile", edit_user_path(current_user) %>
				</li>
				<li class="sair">
					<%= link_to "Sair", logout_path %>
				</li>
			<% else %>
				<li class="novousuario">
					<%= link_to "Registrar", new_user_path %>
				</li>
				<li class="entrar">
					<%= link_to "Entrar", login_path %>
				</li>
	
			<% end %>
		</ul>
            </nav>
</div>

<div class="main-container">
	<div class="loading">
		<%= image_tag "loading.gif" %>
	</div>
	<div class="main wrapper clearfix">
		<article>
			<div id="flash_notice">
				<% if notice.present? %>
					<script type="text/javascript">showNotice("<%= notice %>");</script>
				<% end %>
				<% if alert.present? %>
					<script type="text/javascript">showNotice("<%= alert %>");</script>
				<% end %>
			</div>
			<%= yield %>
		</article>
		<aside>
			<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Aliquam sodales urna non odio egestas tempor. Nunc vel vehicula ante. Etiam bibendum iaculis libero, eget molestie nisl pharetra in. In semper consequat est, eu porta velit mollis nec. Curabitur posuere enim eget turpis feugiat tempor. Etiam ullamcorper lorem dapibus velit suscipit ultrices.</p>
		</aside>
		<div id="main">
			<form>
				<input type="text" id="search">
				<input type="submit" class="solid" value="Pesquisar">
			</form>
		</div>
    </div> <!-- #main -->
</div> <!-- #main-container -->

<div class="footer-container">
	<footer class="wrapper">
		<div class="sitemap">
			<ul>
				<li><%=link_to "Início", {:controller => "page", :action => "inicio"}, {:title=>"Portal DevGeX | O guia do desenvolvedor GeneXus"} %></li>
				<li><%=link_to "Artigos", articles_path, {:title=>"Portal DevGeX | Base de Conhecimentos"} %></li>
				<li><%=link_to "Ideologia", {:controller => "page", :action => "ideologia"}, {:title=>"Portal DevGeX | A idéia por trás do código"} %></li>
				<li><%=link_to "Equipe", {:controller => "page", :action => "equipe"}, {:title=>"Portal DevGeX | Equipe Portal DevGex"} %></li>
				<li><a href="/contato" title="Portal DevGeX | Entre em contato conosco" >Contato</a></li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="copy">
			<p>
				Portal GeneXus &copy; | O guia do desenvolvedor GeneXus.
				<br>
				<p class="genexus">GeneXus e seus produtos são marcas registradas de Artech Consultores SRL.</p>
			</p>
		</div>
    </footer>
</div>
</body>
</html>